10. Managing Firewall and Services

Example production scenario:

Install Apache + open firewall.

---
- name: Setup Apache and firewall
  hosts: all
  become: yes

  tasks:
    - name: Install Apache
      yum:
        name: httpd
        state: present

    - name: Start Apache
      service:
        name: httpd
        state: started

    - name: Allow HTTP in firewall
      firewalld:
        service: http
        permanent: true
        state: enabled

    - name: Reload firewalld
      service:
        name: firewalld
        state: reloaded

Check firewall:

firewall-cmd --list-all
