16. Killing Processes

Example troubleshooting automation.

---
- name: Kill process
  hosts: all

  tasks:
    - name: Find process
      shell: "ps -ef | grep top | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'"
      register: running_process

    - name: Kill process
      shell: "kill {{ item }}"
      loop: "{{ running_process.stdout_lines }}"
      ignore_errors: yes
17. Running Specific Tasks in Playbooks

Run from a specific task:

